OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1782472699
OL,3,CMet Office issues fresh red 'extreme
OL,4,Cheat' warning with excess of 36C in
OL,5,Cshade
OL,7,FThe Met Office has issued another red
OL,8,Fwarning for extreme heat for Friday as
OL,9,Fthe peak of a heatwave affecting most
OL,10,Fof England and Wales are set to shift
OL,11,Feastwards.
OL,13,FFrom midnight tonight until 9pm on
OL,14,FFriday, an additional red warning will
OL,15,Fbe in place across large parts of the
OL,16,FSouth East and the East of England,
OL,17,Fthe forecaster said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
