FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1782472699
OL,3,CMet Office issues fresh red 'extreme
OL,4,Cheat' warning with excess of 36C in
OL,5,Cshade
OL,7,FIn the East of England, the new red
OL,8,Fwarning applies to Central
OL,9,FBedfordshire, Essex, Hertfordshire,
OL,10,FLuton and Thurrock.
OL,12,FMeanwhile in the capital and the South
OL,13,FEast, Bracknell Forest, Brighton and
OL,14,FHove, Buckinghamshire, East Sussex,
OL,15,FGreater London, Hampshire, Kent,
OL,16,FMedway, Milton Keynes, Oxfordshire,
OL,17,FReading, Slough, Surrey, West
OL,18,FBerkshire, West Sussex, Windsor and
OL,19,FMaidenhead, and Wokingham are affected.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
