FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1782472699
OL,3,CMet Office issues fresh red 'extreme
OL,4,Cheat' warning with excess of 36C in
OL,5,Cshade
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,F"Maximum temperatures in the shade
OL,13,Fcould exceed 36C, perhaps rising to
OL,14,F38C in some places," the Met Office
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,F"However, following another very warm
OL,18,Fnight, the greatest likelihood of high
OL,19,Fimpacts are expect to be within this
OL,20,FRed warning area during Friday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
