PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1782472699
OL,3,CMet Office issues fresh red 'extreme
OL,4,Cheat' warning with excess of 36C in
OL,5,Cshade
OL,7,F"The heat will be accompanied by high
OL,8,Fhumidity, exacerbating the potential
OL,9,Ffor discomfort and health impacts,
OL,10,Fwith very warm and humid night times
OL,11,Falso reducing the ability for people
OL,12,Fto recover overnight.
OL,14,F"Significant disruption to daily life
OL,15,Fis likely and the public should take
OL,16,Fevery effort to make precautions and
OL,17,Fadapt their daily routines where
OL,18,Fpossible to cope with these levels of
OL,19,Fheat, which up to now have been
OL,20,Fextremely rare for the UK."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
